<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>

    <title>GitHub Profile Analyzer API</title>

    <style>

        body{

            font-family: Arial;

            max-width:900px;

            margin:auto;

            padding:40px;

            line-height:1.7;

        }

        h1{

            color:#2563eb;

        }

        .endpoint{

            background:#f4f4f4;

            padding:15px;

            border-radius:10px;

            margin-bottom:15px;

        }

        code{

            background:#e5e7eb;

            padding:3px 6px;

            border-radius:5px;

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>🚀 GitHub Profile Analyzer API</h1>

<p>

Analyze GitHub profiles, store insights into MySQL and retrieve them later.

</p>

<hr>

<h2>📌 Available APIs</h2>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Analyze Profile</h3>

<p>

<code>POST /api/analyze/:username</code>

</p>

<p>

Example:

<code>/api/analyze/octocat</code>

</p>

</div>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Get All Profiles</h3>

<p>

<code>GET /api/profiles</code>

</p>

<p>

Pagination:

<code>/api/profiles?page=1</code>

</p>

</div>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Get Single Profile</h3>

<p>

<code>GET /api/profiles/:username</code>

</p>

<p>

Example:

<code>/api/profiles/octocat</code>

</p>

</div>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Search Profiles</h3>

<p>

<code>GET /api/profiles/search</code>

</p>

<p>

Examples:</p>

<ul>

<li>

<code>?username=octo</code>

</li>

<li>

<code>?language=JavaScript</code>

</li>

<li>

<code>?minFollowers=100</code>

</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Search + Sorting</h3>

<p>

<code>/api/profiles/search?language=JavaScript&sort=followers&order=desc</code>

</p>

</div>

<div class="endpoint">

<h3>Rate Limiting</h3>

<p>

Analyze endpoint is protected against excessive requests.

</p>

</div>

<hr>

<p>

Built using Node.js, Express.js, MySQL, GitHub API and deployed on Render.

</p>

</body>

</html>